      "response": "Based on my comprehensive analysis of the LINCE project, here is the final answer:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"primary_language\": \"TypeScript\",\n  \"entry_points\": [\n    \"backend/app/main.py (FastAPI application, router mounting)\",\n    \"frontend/src/App.tsx (main React application component)\",\n    \"frontend/src/api.ts (API client library)\",\n    \"frontend/src/components/MarketChart.tsx (core chart/trading UI component)\",\n    \"android-monitor/app/src/main/java/com/lince/monitor/MainActivity.kt (Android app entry)\"\n  ],\n  \"hotspots\": [\n    \"frontend/src/App.tsx:loadTradingMode (complexity 75)\",\n    \"frontend/src/components/MarketChart.tsx:MarketChart (massive component, ~5200+ lines, all trading chart UI, strategies, indicators)\",\n    \"frontend/src/api.ts:apiFetch (fan_in 29, central API fetch with auth)\",\n    \"frontend/src/api.ts:parseApiError (fan_in 29, error parsing)\",\n    \"backend/app/lince.py:compute_lince (core Lince indicator algorithm using cycle detection)\",\n    \"backend/app/lince.py:get_lince_runtime (orchestrates Lince computation for REST API)\",\n    \"backend/app/routers/trading.py:trading_mobile_arm_lince (remote arm robot order from Android)\",\n    \"frontend/src/utils/chartStrategies.ts (strategy engine for CM, CM-Cross, KAMA-Cross, Lnc, Lnc2)\"\n  ],\n  \"relevant_tests\": [],\n  \"summary\": \"LINCE is a multi-tier algorithmic trading platform for Coinbase. It consists of a TypeScript/React frontend (SPA with real-time charts, order book, trading ticket, ROBOT execution engine, and strategy backtesting/optimization), a Python/FastAPI backend (REST API for market data, trading execution, real-time WebSocket streams, TTS, DB backups, and UI persistence), and an Android/Kotlin companion app (remote monitor with foreground service, alarms, notification overlay, and speech). The project name 'LINCE' refers both to the Lince/Lnc proprietary trading indicator (a cycle-detection algorithm based on price action, sumavol, and trigger bands) and to the robot trading engine that can auto-execute orders when Lince signals fire. The frontend includes advanced chart strategies (CM/SMA cross, EMA/SMA cross, KAMA cross) with built-in optimizer runners that brute-force parameters to maximize profitability. No test files were found in the project.\"\n}\n```",
