      "response": "Now I have gathered all the information needed. Here is my analysis:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"primary_language\": \"Python\",\n  \"entry_points\": [\n    \"backend/app/main.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/full_backfill.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/watch_backfill.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/backfill_public_trades.py\",\n    \"frontend/ (React + TradingView Lightweight Charts dev server)\"\n  ],\n  \"hotspots\": [\n    \"backend/app/lince.py\",\n    \"backend/app/routers/market.py\",\n    \"backend/app/routers/trading.py\",\n    \"backend/app/routers/system.py\",\n    \"backend/app/services/realtime.py\",\n    \"backend/app/services/market.py\",\n    \"backend/app/services/trading.py\",\n    \"backend/app/services/security.py\",\n    \"backend/app/services/storage.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/full_backfill.py\"\n  ],\n  \"relevant_tests\": [\n    \"backend/scripts/full_backfill.py (smoke: --max-cycles 1)\",\n    \"backend/scripts/watch_backfill.py (--once flag for snapshot)\",\n    \"backend/scripts/compact_market_cache.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/backup_sqlite_subset.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/backfill_public_trades.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/backfill_public_trades_historical.py\",\n    \"backend/scripts/offload_public_trades.py\"\n  ],\n  \"summary\": \"LINCE is a local crypto trading system with a TradingView-style architecture. It features a Python FastAPI backend that connects to Coinbase Advanced Trade (REST + WebSocket) and a React frontend with TradingView Lightweight Charts. The core of the project is the proprietary LINCE indicator — a volume-based technical analysis algorithm (compute_lince) that computes cumulative positive/negative volume cycles, trigger levels, and signal probabilities to generate buy/sell signals on crypto pairs (primarily BTC-EUR and BTC-USD). The system supports automated trading via configurable 'robot' profiles (balanced/aggressive/conservative), persistent market data caching in SQLite with incremental sync, real-time WebSocket streaming to the frontend, historical data backfill runners, TTS via ElevenLabs for event alerts, and comprehensive trading security (PIN auth, rate limiting, robot execution authorization). Deployment is managed via systemd services with automated DB backup scripts.\"\n}\n```",
